summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2018 STARCRAFT AUTUMN RIDGE. THE CONTACT RECEIVED NOTIFICATION OF NHTSA CAMPAIGN NUMBER: 19V699000 (ELECTRICAL SYSTEM). THE CONTACT STATED THAT THE MANUFACTURER WAS CONTACTED BY PHONE TO SCHEDULE AN APPOINTMENT WITH THE LOCAL DEALER HOWEVER, THE CONTACT WAS INFORMED THAT DUE TO TECHNICAL ISSUES THE RECALL REPAIR WOULD NOT BE PERFORMED. THE CONTACT WAS INFORMED THAT THERE WAS NO ESTIMATED TIMEFRAME FOR THE RV TO BE REPAIRED. A FAILURE WAS NOT EXPERIENCED AND THE VIN WAS NOT AVAILABLE.
